page.title: 04EXTRACT 520/65 0468
page.content:
MAJOR LAND COVER: {11, 01. AMENITIES: {05, 36.}
{HOUSING:}Modern well planned houses with streets having no through road but cul-de-sacs. Some houses are privately owned and others are rented out by the council. Some areas are still under construction. {POPULATION:}The residential areas contain mostly young families with small children. CLUBS:Many clubs meet in the High School. {COMMUNICATIONS:}There are several public telephones and there are quite a lot of telephone lines crossing the area. There is also a postbox. {FARMING:}Newyearfield farm is very old and the surrounding fields are used for cultivating grass.
